name: Cross Creek (Colorado)
description:
Introduction

This watercourse was fun to downclimb and descend, but is not as narrow or precipitous as other descents in the area. This canyon lies entirely within the Holy Cross Wilderness area. Please follow leave-no-trace techniques if you visit in order to keep this area pristine.
